{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NQELt11PQqMBWAPTXAQETz","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The IPv6 addresses in `tcp6` use the IPv4-mapped IPv6 format: `0000000000000000FFFF0000XXXX`. \n\nLet me decode a few:\n- `0000000000000000FFFF0000B100F40A` → the last 4 bytes: `B1 00 F4 0A` → in little-endian hex: `0AB1 00F4` → but actually the hex string is `0AF4_00B1` when read in normal order...\n\nWait, let me decode properly. The IPv4-mapped IPv6 address has the format `::ffff:x.x.x.x`. \n\nSo for that address, the first 96 bits contain the IPv4-mapped prefix `::ffff:0:0`, and the last 32 bits `B100F40A` represent the IPv4 address in little-endian byte order, which converts to `10.244.0.177`.\n\nSimilarly, the second address decodes to `10.96.164.243`, which is the ClusterIP service. The port `18EB` in hex is 6379, so the original worker has multiple established connections to the ClusterIP service at `10.96.164.243:6379`, which maps to port 10001 on the head node. I'm also seeing connections from the worker directly to the head pod IP at `10.244.0.182` on different high ephemeral ports, bypassing the service entirely. So there are multiple connection paths happening simultaneously—some going through the ClusterIP service and others going straight to the head pod.\n\nThe real question is why GcsClient fails on port 10001 when the Ray client server in proxy mode should theoretically forward all gRPC calls, including GCS service calls, to the head pod. Maybe the proxy isn't handling the GCS service correctly, or there's something specific about how the GCS client authenticates or communicates that breaks through this proxy setup.\n\nSince the established connections to the head pod's GCS port suggest the raylet is successfully using those connections, I should check whether the new worker's IP address itself is the issue—maybe there's a network policy blocking traffic from that specific pod.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1335,"cache_read_input_tokens":85083,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1335},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"34abd7e5-b560-4ada-abf9-16e9c2b88f15","uuid":"299cfd63-d24e-4fda-85a4-b2bb6a639890","request_id":"req_011Cc6fGGoqcKuU4xYLZ7yiX"}
